#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.33"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.33:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.33:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga"
msgstr "4. Deities"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Dutiyaaparihānasutta"
msgstr "33. Non-decline (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.33:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā "
"abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, "
"bhikkhave, sā devatā maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"“Tonight, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, came to me, "
"bowed, stood to one side, and said to me:"

msgctxt "an6.33:1.2"
msgid "‘chayime, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "‘Sir, these six things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant."

msgctxt "an6.33:1.3"
msgid "Katame cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.33:1.4"
msgid ""
"Satthugāravatā, dhammagāravatā, saṅghagāravatā, sikkhāgāravatā, "
"hirigāravatā, ottappagāravatā—"
msgstr ""
"Respect for the Teacher, for the teaching, for the Saṅgha, for the training, "
"for conscience, and for prudence."

msgctxt "an6.33:1.5"
msgid "ime kho, bhante, cha dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī’ti."
msgstr "These six things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant.’"

msgctxt "an6.33:1.6"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, sā devatā."
msgstr "That is what that deity said."

msgctxt "an6.33:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then he bowed and respectfully circled me, keeping me on his right side, "
"before vanishing right there."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.33:2.1"
msgid "Satthugaru dhammagaru,"
msgstr "Respect for the Teacher and the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.33:2.2"
msgid "saṅghe ca tibbagāravo;"
msgstr "and keen respect for the Saṅgha;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.33:2.3"
msgid "Hiriottappasampanno,"
msgstr "having both conscience and prudence,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.33:2.4"
msgid "sappatisso sagāravo;"
msgstr "reverential and respectful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.33:2.5"
msgid "Abhabbo parihānāya,"
msgstr "such a one can’t decline,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.33:2.6"
msgid "nibbānasseva santike”ti."
msgstr "and has drawn near to extinguishment.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.33:2.7"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
